      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what? i'm just a dev trying to fix a crash in a production environment. can you just give me a serious technical breakdown of the tools and methodologies? i don't need the fantasy metaphors, i need to know specifically how to implement valgrind or asan on an embedded target if we're resource constrained.",
